  "title": "Interface ILogger",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogger'>Interface ILogger    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogger.cs#L40'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Core logger interface for logging structured messages with various severity levels.\nImplementations must be thread-safe and support dependency injection.\nAOT-compatible: Uses interfaces and virtual dispatch only.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public interface ILogger</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.Name' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.Name' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogger_Name'>Name    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogger.cs#L45'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the logical name of this logger (typically the component/class name).</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>string Name { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.BeginScope(System.Object)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.BeginScope(System.Object)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogger_BeginScope_System_Object_'>BeginScope(object)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogger.cs#L138'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Begins a named scope for log entries, useful for grouping related logs.\nReturns a disposable that ends the scope when disposed.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>IDisposable BeginScope(object scope)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>scope</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The scope name or identifier.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.idisposable'>IDisposable</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A disposable that removes the scope when disposed.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.GetCorrelationId' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.GetCorrelationId' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogger_GetCorrelationId'>GetCorrelationId()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogger.cs#L130'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the current correlation ID.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>string GetCorrelationId()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The correlation ID, or null if not set.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.IsEnabled(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.IsEnabled(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogger_IsEnabled_Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_LogLevel_'>IsEnabled(LogLevel)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogger.cs#L146'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Determines whether logging is enabled at the given level.\nCan be used to avoid expensive message formatting for disabled levels.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>bool IsEnabled(LogLevel level)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>level</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.html'>LogLevel</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The log level to check.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">True if the level is enabled; fal